March 2023 

Got to meet the legend @handshakesnaketattoos and in return he put me in pain for a few hours. thank you so much for the start of this killer piece, and can’t wait to continue to hate my life in your chair. 
Went to the beach with the @wagewar boys for a week for _____REDACTED* and saw one of the craziest sunsets. 
Got to see my boys @ronniejames___ and @iantaylor__ for _____REDACTED* and got to try all the @strangecandyco hot sauces (pineapple express is supreme)
Saw some friends, made some memories, and that’s that. On to April

July 2023 (so far) 

back out with the incredible @teddyswims camp. running through the UK right now, then off to Australia and maybe some dates in between. summer in the UK isn’t half bad. thanks for looking

Teddy Swims in the United Kingdom - July 2023 - tattoos in Birmingham, sold out show at Roundhouse in London, and watching a building catch fire while eating dinner. supporting @gretavanfleet starting next week, then headed to Australia ✌🏻#fujifilm #frameio #teddyswims

Amsterdam - Hamburg - Denver - Salt Lake City. It’s been a busy week, but band / crew are back in America for a few shows with Greta Van Fleet, then headed off to Australia / New Zealand / Hawaii for a handful of shows #fujifilm #frameio #adobe

Creative Control Tour with The Used
May/June 2023. Filmed / edited by @wheresbryce
Such a bucket list tour for me. If you know me, you know The Used is one of my favorite bands, and to be able to hear their songs nightly and get to create alongside them was an indescribable feeling. The entire band, camp, and team are top notch, and such a please to work with. So grateful for the opportunity. 
Thanks for looking
